# mkfile

> Create one or more empty files of any size
> More information: https://manned.org/mkfile

- Create an empty file of 15 kilobytes:

`mkfile -n {any something} {file something}`

- Create a file of a given size and unit (bytes, KB, MB, GB):

`mkfile -n {any something}{any something} {file something}`

- Create two files of 4 megabytes each:

`mkfile -n {any something} {any something} {any something}`
